'''哈罗德·杰弗里斯爵士'''（{{lang-en|'''Sir Harold Jeffreys'''}}，{{bd|1891年|4月22日|1989年|3月18日}}），英国数学家，统计学家，地球物理学家和天文学家，英國[[皇家學會|皇家學會]]院士<ref name="frs">{{cite journal|title=Sir Harold Jeffreys, 2 April 1891 - 18 March 1989|journal=Biographical Memoirs of Fellows of the Royal Society|date=1990-12-01|doi=10.1098/rsbm.1990.0034|url=http://rsbm.royalsocietypublishing.org/content/roybiogmem/36/301|language=en|volume=36|pages=301–333|issn=0080-4606|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Sir Alan Cook, F. R. S|archive-date=2018-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180601210501/http://rsbm.royalsocietypublishing.org/content/roybiogmem/36/301|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="frs2">{{cite journal|title=Errata|journal=Biographical Memoirs of Fellows of the Royal Society|date=1991-11-01|doi=10.1098/rsbm.1991.0025|url=http://rsbm.royalsocietypublishing.org/content/roybiogmem/37/491|language=en|volume=37|pages=491–491|issn=0080-4606|accessdate=2018-04-02|archive-date=2018-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180602093547/http://rsbm.royalsocietypublishing.org/content/roybiogmem/37/491|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==生平==
他的著作《概率理论》（{{lang|en|''Theory of Probability''}}）首次出版于1939年，在复兴[[贝叶斯概率|贝叶斯概率]]上起到了重要作用<ref name = "jaynes">{{cite book |first=E. T. |last=Jaynes |title=Probability Theory: The Logic of Science |location= |publisher=Cambridge University Press |year=2003 |isbn=0-521-59271-2 }}</ref><ref name="mactutor">{{MacTutor Biography|id=Jeffreys}}</ref>。

